  "description": "<p><span style=\"line-height: 0px;\">﻿</span><strong>据外媒AllThingsD报道，美国移动运营商Verizon周二宣布与谷歌旗下摩托罗拉移动合作，将独家推出三款Droid系列智能手机设备。</strong>三款新智能手机分别为Droid Maxx、Droid Ultra和Droid Mini，均由谷歌旗下摩托罗拉子公司生产。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2f1208e0/sc/23/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245758.htm&amp;t=%E6%91%A9%E6%89%98%E8%81%94%E6%89%8BVerizon%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E4%B8%89%E6%AC%BEDroid%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245758.htm&amp;t=%E6%91%A9%E6%89%98%E8%81%94%E6%89%8BVerizon%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E4%B8%89%E6%AC%BEDroid%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245758.htm&amp;t=%E6%91%A9%E6%89%98%E8%81%94%E6%89%8BVerizon%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E4%B8%89%E6%AC%BEDroid%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245758.htm&amp;t=%E6%91%A9%E6%89%98%E8%81%94%E6%89%8BVerizon%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E4%B8%89%E6%AC%BEDroid%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245758.htm&amp;t=%E6%91%A9%E6%89%98%E8%81%94%E6%89%8BVerizon%